songs.title: Run a Check Up
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: DJ Chose]
I just run a check up
I just run a check
I just run a check up
I just run a check
They know I run a check up
Know I run a check
They know I run a check up
Know I run a check

[Verse 1: Paul Wall]
Louis loafers, Rolex brokers
Hand full of diamonds got them jokers
I am not concerned with you
My necklace got you out of focus
Mixing soda, hocus pocus
Into tripping being posted
Triple cupping watch me pour it
Swinging candy pokers
I'm crawling similar to gofers
[?]
Flyer than a swarm of locusts
Off a Norco and a couple somas
